INSERT INTO `parking_lot_information` VALUES (1, '04031750411870', 'parking lot 1', 1, '<div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"1\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">A parking lot is a place where vehicles are parked. The parking lot includes a simple parking lot that only draws parking grids without management and charges, and there is also a paid parking lot equipped with entry and exit gates, parking administrators, and time cashiers. Modern parking lots often have an automated metered charging system<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%97%AD%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B5%E8%A7%86/784718\" data-lemmaid=\"784718\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">CCTV</a>and video recorder system. The legal responsibility of the parking lot owner and administrator is usually only to provide a place for the driver to park the vehicle, and does not guarantee the liability for vehicle damage and loss. Generally, the contract will be attached<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%A3%E6%9D%A1%E6%AC%BE/1554152\" data-lemmaid=\"1554152\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">Disclaimer</a>It is displayed outside the gate of the parking lot for car owners to refer to.</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">On July 1, 2021, the \"Parking Lot (Garage) Operation Service Specification\" issued by the Beijing Market Supervision and Administration Bureau began to be officially implemented in Beijing.</div><p><br/></p><div class=\"para-title level-3  \" data-index=\"1_1\" label-module=\"para-title\" data-pid=\"4\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal;\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">public parking lot</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"5\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The public parking lot is a paid commercial parking lot (open-air or indoor) built according to urban planning and supporting public buildings for social vehicles. It is called a public parking lot. There are two types of public parking lots: on-street and off-street:</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"6\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">1. On-street temporary public parking lot</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"7\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The on-street temporary parking lot refers to a temporary venue that occupies part of the roads in the city within a specified time limit and allows a large number of vehicles to be parked to meet the needs of large-scale events (parades, rallies, etc.) upon approval.</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"8\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">2. Off-street public parking lot</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"9\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Off-street public parking lots are places other than roads that require investment and construction for parking vehicles, and have the nature of operating fee-based services. Specifically, they are divided into:</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"10\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">1. Transportation parking lot</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"11\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The site specially designed for vehicles to be parked and then transferred to other vehicles is called a transportation parking lot (also known as a transportation hub square). It is generally set up near the vehicle collection and distribution points such as stations (railway stations, rail transit stations, bus hub stations), wharfs, airports, etc., such as the transfer center of the parking lot in the south and north squares of Shanghai Railway Station, the parking lot of Caoxi Road public transport hub, long-distance Passenger bus station, city public transport hub station, etc.</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"12\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">2. Stylistic parking lot</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"13\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The parking spaces specially provided for various cultural and sports activities, cultural entertainment and hospitals are called stylistic parking lots. It is generally installed near large stadiums, theaters, hospitals, conference venues, exhibition venues and tourist attractions.</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"14\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">3. Commercial parking lot</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"15\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The parking lot specially provided for commercial activities, shopping and leisure is called commercial parking lot. It is generally installed near shops, hypermarkets, hotels, etc., such as Grand Gateway Plaza, Meilong Town Plaza, etc.</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"16\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">4. Truck parking lot</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"17\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The parking and maintenance sites specially provided for large trucks, dangerous goods vehicles, container trucks and other vehicles coming to Shanghai from other provinces and cities are called freight vehicle parking lots. It is generally set in the suburban junction. This kind of parking lot is combined with the layout of the cargo distribution center, which is beneficial to the management of cargo loading and unloading, reduces the number of empty trucks on the return journey of freight vehicles, improves transportation efficiency and protects the environment.</div><div class=\"anchor-list \" style=\"position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><a name=\"1_2\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\" href=\"http://\"></a><a name=\"sub16616878_1_2\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\" href=\"http://\"></a><a name=\"Private parking lot\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\" href=\"http://\"></a><a name=\"1-2\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\" href=\"http://\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-3  \" data-index=\"1_2\" label-module=\"para-title\" data-pid=\"18\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal;\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Private parking lot</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"19\" style=\"font-size: 14px; o