tom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">2. Workplace parking lot</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"23\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The parking lot provided for the unit and its employees vehicles is called the workplace parking lot (also known as the units special parking lot). The number of parking spaces depends on the ability of employees to purchase cars. Often, the limited number of parking spaces directly affects the choice of transportation for employees to commute to and from get off work.</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"24\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">3. Special parking lot for freight vehicles</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"25\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The parking and maintenance site for large vehicles, dangerous goods vehicles, trucks, buses and other motor vehicles provided for the business use of the unit is called the freight vehicle parking lot (also known as the professional parking lot of the transportation department).</div><div class=\"anchor-list \" style=\"position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><a name=\"1_3\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\" href=\"http://\"></a><a name=\"sub16616878_1_3\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\" href=\"http://\"></a><a name=\"road car park\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\" href=\"http://\"></a><a name=\"1-3\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\" href=\"http://\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-3  \" data-index=\"1_3\" label-module=\"para-title\" data-pid=\"26\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal;\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">road car park</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"27\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The basic regulations for setting up road parking lots: the permitted parking area is limited, and the specified parking time is limited. It can only be set during non-traffic peak hours and does not affect the smooth traffic (generally set on unbroken sections). It must be adjusted with changes in municipal engineering construction and dynamic traffic. Therefore, the measures of government departments are to set Be careful, the scope will only be gradually reduced, and will not be expanded arbitrarily.</div>');
INSERT INTO `parking_lot_information` VALUES (2, '04031751079409', 'parking lot 2', 2, '<div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"1\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">A parking lot is a place where vehicles are parked. The parking lot includes a simple parking lot that only draws parking grids without management and charges, and there is also a paid parking lot equipped with entry and exit gates, parking administrators, and time cashiers. Modern parking lots often have an automated metered charging system<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%97%AD%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B5%E8%A7%86/784718\" data-lemmaid=\"784718\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">CCTV</a>and video recorder system. The legal responsibility of the parking lot owner and administrator is usually only to provide a place for the driver to park the vehicle, and does not guarantee the liability for vehicle damage and loss. Generally, the contract will be attached<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%A3%E6%9D%A1%E6%AC%BE/1554152\" data-lemmaid=\"1554152\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">Disclaimer</a>It is displayed outside the gate of the parking lot for car owners to refer to.</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">On July 1, 2021, the \"Parking Lot (Garage) Operation Service Specification\" issued by the Beijing Market Supervision and Administration Bureau began to be officially implemented in Beijing.</div><p><br/></p><div class=\"para-title level-3  \" data-index=\"1_1\" label-module=\"para-title\" data-pid=\"4\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal;\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">public parking lot</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"5\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The public parking lot is a paid commercial parking lot (open-air or indoor) built according to urban planning and supporting public buildings for social vehicles. It is called a public parking lot. There are two types of public parking lots: on-street and off-street:</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"6\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">1. On-street temporary public parking lot</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"7\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &q