verflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The special parking lot refers to the parking lot built by the investor outside the road, which is specially used for parking the vehicles of the unit and the residential area. Its setting principles are mostly set according to the needs of building configuration parking spaces and vehicle types of the unit. Generally not open to the outside world, it is a non-commercial special parking lot, which is specifically divided into three types: residential, working, and freight vehicle parking lots.</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"20\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">1. Residential parking lot</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"21\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The parking lot provided for the private car of the owner of the residential area is called the residential parking lot (also known as the community parking lot).</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"22\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">2. Workplace parking lot</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"23\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The parking lot provided for the unit and its employees vehicles is called the workplace parking lot (also known as the units special parking lot). The number of parking spaces depends on the ability of employees to purchase cars. Often, the limited number of parking spaces directly affects the choice of transportation for employees to commute to and from get off work.</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"24\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">3. Special parking lot for freight vehicles</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"25\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The parking and maintenance site for large vehicles, dangerous goods vehicles, trucks, buses and other motor vehicles provided for the business use of the unit is called the freight vehicle parking lot (also known as the professional parking lot of the transportation department).</div><div class=\"anchor-list \" style=\"position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><a name=\"1_3\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\" href=\"http://\"></a><a name=\"sub16616878_1_3\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\" href=\"http://\"></a><a name=\"road car park\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\" href=\"http://\"></a><a name=\"1-3\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\" href=\"http://\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-3  \" data-index=\"1_3\" label-module=\"para-title\" data-pid=\"26\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal;\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">road car park</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"27\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The basic regulations for setting up road parking lots: the permitted parking area is limited, and the specified parking time is limited. It can only be set during non-traffic peak hours and does not affect the smooth traffic (generally set on unbroken sections). It must be adjusted with changes in municipal engineering construction and dynamic traffic. Therefore, the measures of government departments are to set Be careful, the scope will only be gradually reduced, and will not be expanded arbitrarily.</div>');
INSERT INTO `parking_lot_information` VALUES (3, '04031751171798', 'parking lot 3', 3, '<div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"1\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">A parking lot is a place where vehicles are parked. The parking lot includes a simple parking lot that only draws parking grids without management and charges, and there is also a paid parking lot equipped with entry and exit gates, parking administrators, and time cashiers. Modern parking lots often have an automated metered charging system<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%97%AD%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B5%E8%A7%86/784718\" data-lemmaid=\"784718\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">CCTV</a>and video recorder system. The legal responsibility of the parking lot owner and administrator is usually only to provide a place for the driver to park the vehicle, and does not guarantee the liability for vehicle damage and loss. Generally, the contract will be attached<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%A3%E6%9D%A1%E6%AC%BE/1554152\" data-lemmaid=\"1554152\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">Disclaimer</a>It is displayed outside the gate of the parking lot for car owners to refer to.</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">On July 1, 2021, the \"Parking Lot (Garage) Operation Service Specification\" issued by the Beijing Market Supervision and Administration Bureau began to be officially implemented in Beijing.</div><p><br/></p><div class=\"para-title level-3  \" data-index=\"1_1\" label-module=\"para-title\" data-pid=\"4\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal;\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">public parking lot</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"5\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The public parking lot is a paid commercial parking lot (open-air or indoor) built according to urban planning and supporting public buildings for social vehicles. It is called a public parking lot. There are two types of public parking lots: on-street and off-street:</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"6\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">1. On-street temporary public parking lot</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"7\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The on-street temporary parking lot refers to a temporary venue that occupies part of the roads in the city within a specified time limit and allows a large number of vehicles to be parked to meet the needs of large-scale events (parades, rallies, etc.) upon approval.</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"8\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">2. Off-street public parking lot</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"9\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Off-street public parking lots are places other than roads that require investment and construction for parking vehicles, and have the nature of operating fee-based services. Specifically, they are divided into:</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"10\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">1. Transportation parking lot</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\