stadiums, theaters, hospitals, conference venues, exhibition venues and tourist attractions.</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"14\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">3. Commercial parking lot</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"15\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The parking lot specially provided for commercial activities, shopping and leisure is called commercial parking lot. It is generally installed near shops, hypermarkets, hotels, etc., such as Grand Gateway Plaza, Meilong Town Plaza, etc.</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"16\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">4. Truck parking lot</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"17\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The parking and maintenance sites specially provided for large trucks, dangerous goods vehicles, container trucks and other vehicles coming to Shanghai from other provinces and cities are called freight vehicle parking lots. It is generally set in the suburban junction. This kind of parking lot is combined with the layout of the cargo distribution center, which is beneficial to the management of cargo loading and unloading, reduces the number of empty trucks on the return journey of freight vehicles, improves transportation efficiency and protects the environment.</div><div class=\"anchor-list \" style=\"position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><a name=\"1_2\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\" href=\"http://\"></a><a name=\"sub16616878_1_2\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\" href=\"http://\"></a><a name=\"Private parking lot\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\" href=\"http://\"></a><a name=\"1-2\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\" href=\"http://\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-3  \" data-index=\"1_2\" label-module=\"para-title\" data-pid=\"18\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal;\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Private parking lot</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"19\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The special parking lot refers to the parking lot built by the investor outside the road, which is specially used for parking the vehicles of the unit and the residential area. Its setting principles are mostly set according to the needs of building configuration parking spaces and vehicle types of the unit. Generally not open to the outside world, it is a non-commercial special parking lot, which is specifically divided into three types: residential, working, and freight vehicle parking lots.</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"20\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">1. Residential parking lot</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"21\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The parking lot provided for the private car of the owner of the residential area is called the residential parking lot (also known as the community parking lot).</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"22\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">2. Workplace parking lot</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"23\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The parking lot provided for the unit and its employees vehicles is called the workplace parking lot (also known as the units special parking lot). The number of parking spaces depends on the ability of employees to purchase cars. Often, the limited number of parking spaces directly affects the choice of transportation for employees to commute to and from get off work.</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"24\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">3. Special parking lot for freight vehicles</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"25\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The parking and maintenance site for large vehicles, dangerous goods vehicles, trucks, buses and other motor vehicles provided for the business use of the unit is called the freight vehicle parking lot (also known as the professional parking lot of the transportation department).</div><div class=\"anchor-list \" style=\"position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><a name=\"1_3\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\" href=\"http://\"></a><a name=\"sub16616878_1_3\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\" href=\"http://\"></a><a name=\"road car park\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\" href=\"http://\"></a><a name=\"1-3\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\" href=\"http://\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-3  \" data-index=\"1_3\" label-module=\"para-title\" data-pid=\"26\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal;\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">road car park</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" data-pid=\"27\" style=\"font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The basic regulations for setting up road parking lots: the permitted parking area is limited, and the specified parking time is limited. It can only be set during non-traffic peak hours and does not affect the smooth traffic (generally set on unbroken sections). It must be adjusted with changes in municipal engineering construction and dynamic traffic. Therefore, the measures of government departments are to set Be careful, the scope will only be gradually reduced, and will not be expanded arbitrarily.</div>');

